panels.name: Events by Region Trend
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=*cloudtrail* "redshift.amazonaws.com"
| json field=_raw "awsRegion"
| json field=_raw "eventSource" nodrop
| json field=_raw "eventName" nodrop
| parse "\"clusterIdentifier\":\"*\"" as clusterIdentifier nodrop
| where eventSource = "redshift.amazonaws.com"
| timeslice 15m
| count by awsRegion, _timeslice
| transpose row _timeslice column awsRegion
